Apple has <a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/retail/umeda/">announced</a> that it will be opening an all-new store at the Grand Front shopping complex in Osaka, Japan, on Saturday, July 26.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/07/Apple-Umeda-Wallpaper.jpg" alt="" width="1244" height="700" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1009028" /><br/>
To celebrate the occasion, Apple has shared a <a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/main/umeda/WFeQBylL/images/storepage/wallpaper/umeda_wallpaper_mobile.png">wallpaper for the iPhone</a>, <a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/main/umeda/WFeQBylL/images/storepage/wallpaper/umeda_wallpaper_tablet.png">iPad</a>, and <a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/main/umeda/WFeQBylL/images/storepage/wallpaper/umeda_wallpaper_desktop.png">Mac</a>.<br/>
<br/>
This will be Apple's first store in Umeda, a busy mixed-use district of Osaka with two major train stations, shops, restaurants, and more.<br/>
<br/>
Apple has another store in Osaka, <a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/retail/shinsaibashi/">in the Shinsaibashi district</a>.<div class="linkback">Tag: <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/guide/apple-store/">Apple Store</a></div><br/>This article, &quot;<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/07/03/apple-umeda-japan-wallpaper/">Apple Celebrates All-New Store With iPhone, iPad, and Mac Wallpaper</a>&quot; first appeared on <a href="https://www.macrumors.com">MacRumors.com</a><br/><br/><a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/apple-celebrates-all-new-store-with-iphone-ipad-and-mac-wallpaper.2460100/">Discuss this article</a> in our forums<br/><br/>